<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 12:20:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>香港立法会一致通过新国安法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-legislature-unanimously-passes-new-national-security-law-2024-03-19/</link><description>香港立法会议员周二一致通过了一项新的国家安全法案，在该法案提出两周内，快速推进了一项重要立法，批评者称该法案进一步威胁了这座中国统治城市的自由。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 11:05:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-legislature-unanimously-passes-new-national-security-law-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国蚂蚁集团任命新总裁，这是监管改革以来最大规模的人事变动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-ant-group-appoints-new-president-biggest-reshuffle-since-regulatory-2024-03-19/</link><description>据一位周二看到蚂蚁集团首席执行官兼董事长井贤栋内部电子邮件的消息人士透露，韩信谊将成为中国蚂蚁集团总裁，该金融科技公司的一些部门将成立自己的董事会，以更加独立地运营。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 10:56:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-ant-group-appoints-new-president-biggest-reshuffle-since-regulatory-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>香港立法会三读通过国安法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-legislature-passes-third-reading-national-security-bill-2024-03-19/</link><description>香港立法会议员周二通过了新的国家安全法案三读，距离全面通过又近了一步。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 10:53:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-legislature-passes-third-reading-national-security-bill-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本从颠倒的世界中回归，人工智能开始发力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-19/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 10:25:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>由于市场竞争加剧，小鹏汽车预测季度收入低于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-forecast-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-2024-03-19/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商小鹏汽车周二预测第一季度营收低于市场预期，原因是经济低迷和激烈竞争抑制了汽车需​​求。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 10:08:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-forecast-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>随着世界杯预赛的恢复，亚洲冠军卡塔尔队转移焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/asian-champions-qatar-shift-focus-world-cup-preliminaries-resume-2024-03-19/</link><description>卡塔尔将于周四对阵科威特，恢复首次世界杯预选赛的资格，教练席稳定，但在本土卫冕亚洲杯六周后，球场上的情况发生了变化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 09:58:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/asian-champions-qatar-shift-focus-world-cup-preliminaries-resume-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>行业高管表示，太阳能电池板价格将在两年内保持低位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/solar-panel-prices-remain-low-up-two-years-says-industry-exec-2024-03-19/</link><description>马来西亚一位行业高管周二表示，太阳能电池板的价格在过去 12 个月内几乎减半，并将在两年内保持在当前水平。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 09:41:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/solar-panel-prices-remain-low-up-two-years-says-industry-exec-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>智能手机销量强劲，小米营收增长 11%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-xiaomi-q4-2023-revenue-rises-11-beats-estimates-2024-03-19/</link><description>中国小米公布第四季度收入增长 10.9%，由于智能手机销售强劲，该行业显示出复苏迹象，调整后净利润超出预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 09:39:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-xiaomi-q4-2023-revenue-rises-11-beats-estimates-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis首席执行官表示，意大利应该在激励措施上走法国路线</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-should-take-french-route-incentives-stellantis-ceo-says-2024-03-19/</link><description>Stellantis首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯(Carlos Tavares)周二在接受《il Resto del Carlino》报纸采访时表示，意大利在审查自己的国家计划时应该效仿法国目前的汽车购买激励措施，即有利于欧洲生产的汽车。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 09:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-should-take-french-route-incentives-stellantis-ceo-says-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>印花税取消后，内地人涌入香港房地产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/mainland-chinese-surge-into-hong-kong-property-after-stamp-duties-scrapped-2024-03-19/</link><description>在经历了三年多的大流行引发的平静之后，中国大陆人开始在香港抢购房屋，在香港取消对外国买家的所有额外印花税几周后，中国内地人在香港新房销售中占比高达三分之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 09:02:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/mainland-chinese-surge-into-hong-kong-property-after-stamp-duties-scrapped-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>独家：普京将于五月访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russias-putin-visit-china-may-sources-2024-03-19/</link><description>据五位知情人士透露，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京将于五月前往中国与习近平举行会谈，这可能是这位克里姆林宫领导人在新总统任期内的首次海外访问。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 08:45:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russias-putin-visit-china-may-sources-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>印度称中国对阿鲁纳恰尔邦的主权主张“荒谬”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-calls-china-defence-ministrys-claims-over-arunachal-pradesh-state-absurd-2024-03-19/</link><description>印度外交部周二表示，中国对阿鲁纳恰尔邦提出“荒谬的主张”，并补充说，与中国接壤的东北部邦将永远是“印度不可分割的一部分”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 08:30:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-calls-china-defence-ministrys-claims-over-arunachal-pradesh-state-absurd-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>随着出生率下降，中国许多医院停止新生儿接生服务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/many-hospitals-china-stop-newborn-delivery-services-birth-rate-drops-2024-03-19/</link><description>据官方媒体《每日经济新闻》报道，中国许多医院今年已停止提供新生儿接生服务，行业专家警告称，由于新生儿数量创纪录下降，需求下降，将导致“产科寒冬”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 07:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/many-hospitals-china-stop-newborn-delivery-services-birth-rate-drops-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国青少年被杀事件让农民工“留守”子女成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/killing-teen-china-puts-left-behind-children-migrant-workers-spotlight-2024-03-19/</link><description>上周，中国北方一名13岁男孩被杀，三名男孩被警方拘留，引发了媒体对青少年犯罪和农民工留守儿童困境的热议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 06:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/killing-teen-china-puts-left-behind-children-migrant-workers-spotlight-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商万科的信贷追求因要求抵押品的呼声而蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-developer-vankes-credit-pursuit-clouded-by-clamour-collateral-2024-03-19/</link><description>北京方面罕见地发布了一项旨在帮助万科应对流动性危机的指令，这使得贷款机构争先恐后地争夺这家国有开发商提议作为抵押品的资产，而各方则竭尽全力阻止房地产行业的恶化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 06:25:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-developer-vankes-credit-pursuit-clouded-by-clamour-collateral-2024-03-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>